    * Add, log4j-api and log4j-core maven dependency.

    * Create log4j2.xml configuration file. Sample XML - https://howtodoinjava.com/log4j2/log4j2-xml-configuration-example/
    * IMP: Create a Directory at Main/Resources. Add log4j2.xml file into this directory.
